<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>CONFIG-ORI&Oacute;N | Sistema para la configuraci&oacute;n del mecanismo de rastreo de Ori&oacute;n 2.0</title>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
